text: Miguel de la Borda is a corregimiento in Donoso District, Colón Province, Panama with a population of 2,326 as of 2010. It is the seat of Donoso District. Its population as of 1990 was 2,218; its population as of 2000 was 2,052. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Colón Province Category:Road- inaccessible communities of Panama
title: Miguel de la Borda
